content.rendered:
Directed by Ranjit Tewari.

Written by Ranjit Tewari. Aseem Arrora.

Cast Farhan Akhtar(Kishan Mohan Girhotra). Abhinay Raj Singh(Prabhat Son). Diana Penty(Gayatri Kashyap). Inaamulhaq(Dikkat Ansari). Ronit Roy(Jailer). Gippy Grewal(Parminder Singh Gill). Deepak Dobriyal(Victor Chattopadhyay). Rajesh Sharma(Purushottam Madan Pandit). Naushaad Abbas(Cop). Sanjay Bhatia(Police Officer). Samridhi Dewan(Veera).Vineet Gill.Tareeq Ahmed Khan. Ravi Kishan(Pawan Singh Chaturvedi).Yash Kumar. Sukh Kunwar(Pali). Tiwari Nirmal(Charausiya). Alok Pandey(Bunty).Raj Patra.Nadeem Sheikh. Ajay Kumar Singh(IAS Officer).Manish Singh.Uday Tikekar.Manoj Tiwari. Manwendra Tripathy(Shashtri).Daksh Vashisht

Language Hindi.

Producers Monisha Advani. Nikkhil Advani. Ajit Andhare. Madhu Bhojwani. Hemraj Dogra. Karan Joshi. Jaswinder Pabbla. Sarita Patil. Satish Poddar. Rameshchandra Yadav.

Production Emmay Entertainment. Viacom18 Motion Pictures.
